parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag to deploy in a crash can increase the risk of serious injury or death to the driver and passengers.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seatbelt to lock or restrain the occupant can increase the risk of serious injury or death in a crash.
